lead_paragraph: Agnieszka Radwanska registered an unusually comfortable third-round win over France's Caroline Garcia at the U.S. Open on Saturday, but the Polish fourth seed hungers for more at Flushing Meadows.

headline.print_headline: Radwanska Rolls Into Fourth Round, Hungry for More
